1. Allowed:
1.1. Redistribution of raw data. 
1.2. Deriving new metrics.
1.3. Distribution of derived metrics. 
1.4. Usage for public good.
1.5. Usage for the machine learning. 

2. If you want to use the data for non-profit activities credits of the source is mandatory.

3. If you want to use the data for for-profit activities contact info@pilsetacilvekiem.lv for terms and conditions.

4. Forbidden:
4.1. Modification of the raw data.
4.2. Distribution of the modified source data. 
